{"tid":717526,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"當年被偷金球獎　米基爾報復美斯啱時辰","createTime":"2018-06-26T05:51:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T06:23:11.000Z","uid":4661,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d1d23085b76f4cac6ee0660a8f952b51c3df9f66","tid":717526,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T05:51:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/nigeria.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/nigeria.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/nigeria.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180626/photo/bkn-20180626124245462-0626_00882_001_01p.jpg?20180626130016\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180626%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180626124245462-0626_00882_001_01p.jpg%3F20180626130016&h=8a0ef593&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尼日利亞今晚面對阿根廷進行D組生死戰，效力FC天津的中場約翰米基爾，繼當年世青盃再同美斯對決。 <br />\n<br />\n約翰米基爾現時成就當然同美斯差天共地，但早於2005年世青盃，大家仍未成名時，當年嘅米基爾表現毫不遜色，佢更加認定當年係美斯搶走自己嘅金球獎：「美斯當年偷走我嘅金球獎！人人都話我會攞，但決戰阿根廷時，美斯入兩球協助阿根廷贏2比1，得獎人獎就變為佢。」往事如煙，今仗只要尼日利亞擊敗阿根廷，送美斯一程，咁就係米基爾嘅最佳報復。"},{"pid":"e76facb2ae2753f0e0b68a1dfaced9c621754ced","tid":717526,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T05:52:17.000Z","msg":"學英文<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/football/2018/jun/25/mikel-john-obi-lionel-messi-nigeria-argentina-world-cup\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ffootball%2F2018%2Fjun%2F25%2Fmikel-john-obi-lionel-messi-nigeria-argentina-world-cup&d=vt%2BzeEWJDyQQW7dzOCDrYZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=fb4a19c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/football/2018/jun/25/mikel-john-obi-lionel-messi-nigeria-argentina-world-cup</a>"},{"pid":"3950bd74e8aaac62da6d9bdca425186519617523","tid":717526,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T05:55:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservic